high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the round table, the hang a right and walk up to the side of the coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the end of the coffee table.
Put the watch in the closest cardboard box on the coffee table.
Pick up the cardboard box with the watch in it off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk over to the round table.
Put the cardboard box with the watch in it on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a watch in it on a round table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the round table then turn right and walk to the coffee table with two boxes on it.
Pick up the watch from the coffee table.
Move to the left side of the coffee table.
Put the watch in the box that is on the left side of the table.
Pick up the box with the watch inside from the coffee table.
Turn right and walk to the round table with the tablecloth.
Put the box on the table to the left of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a watch inside on the round table.

high_descs: Turn to the right, then right again and face the coffee table.
Pick up the watch from the center of the coffee table.
Carry the watch and move left, and face the coffee table on the right.
Place the watch inside the box.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Carry the box and turn to the right to find the round table.
Place the box on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Move a watch and box to a table.
